The paper discusses views over RDF datasets, which are commonly used in data management systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases). The paper also discusses the application of view definition mechanisms to different scenarios, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses query modularization, which is a software engineering (cs.SE) topic. Finally, the paper discusses query answering, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR).
